30:30.563 --> 30:32.362
I can't!

30:32.364 --> 30:34.932
I have already shared my plans
to prosecute them.

30:34.934 --> 30:38.335
With mary? Explain to her
that you have changed your mind.

30:38.337 --> 30:40.337
And make sure
she believes you,

30:40.339 --> 30:43.874
Because if the people learn
that you killed your father,

30:43.876 --> 30:45.843
They will never believe
your queen didn't know it.

30:45.845 --> 30:47.511
Your heads will be on

30:47.513 --> 30:50.247
Two pikes side by side.

30:50.249 --> 30:54.117
I know you're both
very romantic,

30:54.119 --> 30:56.587
But I doubt this is the future
together you had in mind.

31:04.295 --> 31:07.064
Francis, why? We spoke
of this only hours ago.

31:07.066 --> 31:09.967
I simply changed my mind.
You will only

31:09.969 --> 31:12.536
Inflame the protestants further.

31:12.538 --> 31:14.905
The violence
will get worse!

31:14.907 --> 31:21.278
Yes, and I heard your opinion,
and I... I simply disagree.

31:21.280 --> 31:23.947
The burning of catholic shops
is not my opinion.

31:23.949 --> 31:27.251
The murder of that protestant
boy was <i>not</i> my opinion!

31:27.253 --> 31:29.386
Mary, I have already
made my decision.

31:29.388 --> 31:33.290
I'm informing the court now in
writing, before greer's wedding.

31:33.292 --> 31:36.126
My people will know of my
decision before the day's end.

31:36.128 --> 31:38.128
<i>Your</i> people?

31:38.130 --> 31:39.997
I thought we were
to rule together.

31:39.999 --> 31:43.000
At our coronation, you said
we would rule as a partnership.

31:43.002 --> 31:46.136
Mary, I can't always
be your husband first.

31:46.138 --> 31:47.638
Sometimes I have to be king.

31:47.640 --> 31:49.506
Francis, this isn't like you.

31:49.508 --> 31:51.141
Tell me what's

31:51.143 --> 31:53.410
Going on,
what's wrong.

31:53.412 --> 31:54.511
We have to get
to greer's wedding.

31:54.513 --> 31:56.446
Francis!

32:11.629 --> 32:14.531
Honestly, is greer
drawing out the suspense

32:14.533 --> 32:16.700
To make a grander entrance?

32:16.702 --> 32:20.070
Will she be arriving
on flying swans?

32:20.072 --> 32:22.105
Excuse me.

