We were out
on the ocean, sailing,

33:38.417 --> 33:41.284
And a school of dolphins
swam up all around us.

33:41.286 --> 33:42.619
Really?
Now,

33:42.621 --> 33:44.187
They were so close, so wild,

33:44.189 --> 33:45.722
And one of them raised its head

33:45.724 --> 33:47.691
And looked at me
as if he could

33:47.693 --> 33:49.126
Say something.

33:49.128 --> 33:51.161
Uh, sorry.

33:51.163 --> 33:52.529
Uh, what a wonder.

33:52.531 --> 33:55.098
And what would he have
said, if he could?

33:55.100 --> 33:57.434
"I understand more
than you think,

33:57.436 --> 33:59.803
And it thrills me to see you."

33:59.805 --> 34:04.074
Lady lola, I can't
promise dolphins,

34:04.076 --> 34:06.276
But is there any chance

34:06.278 --> 34:08.678
I could take you out
sailing tomorrow?

34:08.680 --> 34:10.347
Lola.

34:10.349 --> 34:12.482
I've been meaning
to congratulate you.

34:12.484 --> 34:14.284
Magnificent christening
of your son.

34:14.286 --> 34:15.719
Baron john phillip.

34:15.721 --> 34:18.388
The king was beaming,
so proud of his son.

34:18.390 --> 34:20.090
Aris:
Oh, I didn't realize.

34:20.092 --> 34:21.792
You're the mother
of the new baron.

34:21.794 --> 34:24.394
That's me, one and the same.

34:24.396 --> 34:26.396
Well, let me offer
my congratulations, as well.

34:26.398 --> 34:28.198
And I must apologize.

34:28.200 --> 34:30.500
It slipped my memory.
I'm leaving

34:30.502 --> 34:32.335
At first light,
so, sadly,

34:32.337 --> 34:34.638
I should retire.

34:37.542 --> 34:40.377
What was that
piece of theater?

34:40.379 --> 34:42.212
You deliberately
drove him away.

34:42.214 --> 34:44.347
I deliberately saved you
valuable time and energy.

34:44.349 --> 34:47.117
Aris doesn't have
the mettle for you.

34:47.119 --> 34:50.821
Other men will be afraid
of getting close to you

34:50.823 --> 34:53.123
Because they see you
as the king's property.

34:53.125 --> 34:55.459
Oh, I don't see you like that.

34:55.461 --> 34:58.662
But unlike most men,
I'm not afraid of the king.

34:58.664 --> 35:02.099
In fact, I suspect francis is
somewhat afraid of me.

35:02.101 --> 35:03.400
Oh, so am I.

35:03.402 --> 35:05.235
And men are afraid of you,

35:05.237 --> 35:07.504
So we're both feared.

35:07.506 --> 35:09.473
Can be quite isolating,
can't it?

35:10.708 --> 35:13.577
It can leave one... Lonely.

35:13.579 --> 35:15.479
That's presumptuous of you.

35:15.481 --> 35:16.847
And yet it's true.

35:18.449 --> 35:21.284
So, why don't we get
to know one another?

35:21.286 --> 35:23.420
What?

35:23.422 --> 35:24.654
Over tea.
Tea?

35:24.656 --> 35:26.289
You don't like tea?

35:26.291 --> 35:27.424
I don't like <i>you.</i>

35:27.426 --> 35:28.658
You don't know me.

35:28.660 --> 35:31.661
I know a little.
Well, that's more than most.

35:32.597 --> 35:36.133
A very... Odd but kind offer.

35:36.135 --> 35:38.301
Regrettably, I must decline.

35:38.303 --> 35:42.439
Well, it's an open invitation.

35:42.441 --> 35:45.442
Xavier, you old ghost.

35:45.444 --> 35:47.277
Lola:
The butterfly.

35:47.279 --> 35:48.612
Where have you been
hiding yourself?

35:48.614 --> 35:50.180
Come.

35:56.554 --> 35:58.788
I was certain
I'd been abandoned.

35:58.790 --> 36:00.490
What changed you?

36:00.492 --> 36:06.530
I've spent my life grasping
for security, safety.

36:06.532 --> 36:08.365
I've lived in fear
of the future,

36:08.367 --> 36:10.400
Of what people
might think of me

36:10.402 --> 36:11.701
And how that could help

36:11.703 --> 36:13.570
Or hurt me and my family.

36:13.572 --> 36:17.407
But you offer something
more interesting,

36:17.409 --> 36:19.776
Something more challenging.

36:19.778 --> 36:22.546
You stand by your convictions
and principles,

36:22.548 --> 36:24.548
You strive to make the world
what it should be,

36:24.550 --> 36:26.583
Not insulate yourself from it.

36:26.585 --> 36:28.785
I will protect you.

36:28.787 --> 36:30.587
And I you.

36:37.428 --> 36:39.663
(laughing)

36:49.507 --> 36:51.341
I love you.

36:53.611 --> 36:55.712
I need you to know that.

36:55.714 --> 36:58.481
I do.

36:58.483 --> 36:59.950
And I want to support you.

36:59.952 --> 37:02.419
As your wife,
as your queen.

37:02.421 --> 37:04.788
But I can't understand why
you would let the murderers

37:04.790 --> 37:06.356
Of that boy walk free.

37:06.358 --> 37:07.824
You know
that this a larger issue.

37:07.826 --> 37:10.860
I understand that we have
to bow to catholic nobles

37:10.862 --> 37:12.662
Who pretend to bow to us.

37:12.664 --> 37:14.998
My own nation has fallen
to protestantism.

37:15.000 --> 37:17.801
But you could have held
those catholics accountable.

37:17.803 --> 37:20.537
What they did is only going
to inflame the protestants.

37:20.539 --> 37:22.005
I can't talk about this anymore.

37:22.007 --> 37:23.506
He was just a boy.

37:23.508 --> 37:24.975
Mary, stop.
The nephew

37:24.977 --> 37:26.376
Of your friend, your cousin.

37:26.378 --> 37:27.744
The decision is made,
it is done.

37:27.746 --> 37:29.279
I am begging you to let it go.

37:29.281 --> 37:32.682
Why can't we discuss this?
We used to.

37:32.684 --> 37:34.284
It's not always possible.

37:34.286 --> 37:35.552
Why, in this instance,

37:35.554 --> 37:37.988
Is that the case?
What has changed?

37:37.990 --> 37:39.756
Francis,
what aren't you telling me?

37:39.758 --> 37:41.858
It is a choice I made as king.

37:41.860 --> 37:43.727
A choice
that we discussed thoroughly.

37:43.729 --> 37:45.528
You just don't agree with it.

37:45.530 --> 37:47.731
There's something else going on.

37:47.733 --> 37:49.699
Lately you've been
distant,

37:49.701 --> 37:53.370
Acting as though
you're haunted by something.

37:53.372 --> 37:55.705
I need peace

37:55.707 --> 37:57.374
And quiet.

37:57.376 --> 37:59.276
You need to trust me!

37:59.278 --> 38:00.610
To share
things with me.

38:00.612 --> 38:02.946
Not everything can be solved
by talking,

38:02.948 --> 38:04.681
By love, by you.

38:04.683 --> 38:08.585
There are things we cannot
change, that cannot be undone.

38:08.587 --> 38:10.487
Things that I don't tell you
to protect you.

38:10.489 --> 38:11.855
Protect me from what?!

38:11.857 --> 38:13.957
I have already said too much.

38:13.959 --> 38:16.293
You have said
far too little!

38:16.295 --> 38:17.761
Mary, please.
What could possibly

38:17.763 --> 38:19.629
Endanger me so much
that I shouldn't know about it?

38:19.631 --> 38:20.964
Don't.

38:20.966 --> 38:22.666
What is this mystery threat

38:22.668 --> 38:23.867
That somehow involves
your son's nanny,

38:23.869 --> 38:25.468
That has you skulking
around the castle

38:25.470 --> 38:27.570
At odd hours?

38:28.739 --> 38:30.940
Something I can't fix.

38:30.942 --> 38:33.677
Something that
you can't change.

38:33.679 --> 38:36.379
These secret visits
to your son...

38:36.381 --> 38:38.315
And the baby
that I lost...

38:38.317 --> 38:41.384
You worry that I can't do it.

38:43.387 --> 38:45.322
Do you worry
that I can't bear you a child?

38:45.324 --> 38:47.057
Yes.

38:47.059 --> 38:48.992
I worry because,

38:48.994 --> 38:50.660
As a king and a man,
I want heirs.

38:50.662 --> 38:52.062
Is that what you want to hear?

38:52.064 --> 38:54.030
Does it bring us closer
for you to know that

38:54.032 --> 38:57.400
Your failure disappoints me
beyond words?

39:01.405 --> 39:03.773
Have I answered you fully?

39:03.775 --> 39:06.609
Are we done with this
relentless interrogation?

39:06.611 --> 39:09.579
You told me
you hadn't lost hope.

39:09.581 --> 39:12.382
I lied.

39:14.518 --> 39:16.753
Mary, I'm sorry.
I shouldn't have.

39:16.755 --> 39:18.955
I wish...

39:18.957 --> 39:21.591
For something
that I can't give you.

39:25.429 --> 39:27.364
But I asked you for the truth,

39:27.366 --> 39:29.866
And you certainly gave it to me.

39:31.469 --> 39:33.670
I don't need to hear any more.

